<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-defence> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "We work for a secure and prosperous United Kingdom with global reach and influence. We will protect our people, territories, values and interests at home and overseas, through strong armed forces and in partnership with allies, to ensure our security, support our national interests and safeguard our prosperity. MOD is a ministerial department, supported by 24 agencies and public bodies ."@en .
